</style><p>この度の 谷郷さんのグッズモデルからの引退には、惜しむ声を中心に、国内外から様々な反響が寄せられており、X (Twitter) のトレンドにも一時「YAGOO」が入っております。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/natsuiromatsuri/status/1708659744532283486" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHcXq8MgXS0lT-Yz-Q9b82P0-O7mjhzqljL66gSXTyMXjxMOIuHJAchYj88VChnSaamr1OPloO5MR3K1_KByXe5RCFf1htjcBix2MP6QlBzN2CbSSsV_FKTfaIBKwCkBsLA1RBMj5frSHsMhh8OukS7J=w1097-h1483-s-no" alt=""/></a></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/natsuiromatsuri/status/1708675812315296096" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHcFlo-jxfX2rKsLtUSED_ZSG3WYjI3Mp-9-s48maL3gl8xBPbHo46t8RXXm-OS3PVuzScFHVNwaDMZHO-IFdtngcaa8VtemxTq0oQf0EACNW8Es8mTIQEbg4VY0p3aWuAWEnkmbLwnvO8c-8iPSjRcE=w1097-h549-s-no" alt=""/></a></figure><p></p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://twitter.com/tanigox" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="YAGOO / Motoaki Tanigo">YAGOO / Motoaki Tanigo</a></p> <cite>X (Twitter)</cite></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">ホロライブプロダクション公式サイト</a></p><cite>カバー株式会社</cite></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://cover-corp.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="カバー株式会社">カバー株式会社</a></p><cite>公式サイト</cite></blockquote><p>( <em>P2y.jp 管理代表者「2号さん (仮)」</em> ／バーチャル・メタバース・VTuber情報) </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Vt66A2Fw3Y"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/cover-corporation-ceo-tanigo-motoaki-retirement-from-hololive-production-goods-model/">COVER Corporation&#39;s CEO Tanigo Motoaki “Retirement from hololive Production&#39;s Goods Model”</a> </blockquote>